# Mirellé — /shop Route System Knowledge Prompt
# Use this as context for any agent writing shop posts or working on the shop system.

---

## SITE OVERVIEW

- **Site:** Mirellé (mirelleinspo.com) — a nail inspiration and editorial blog
- **Stack:** Next.js (App Router), TypeScript, Tailwind CSS, MDX/MD content
- **Colors:** Background `#f9fafb`, Foreground `#252220`. No pink/accent colors in shop.
- **Fonts:** `font-heading` (Larken), `font-body` (Crimson Text), `font-ui` (General Sans)
- **Prose class for content:** `prose-content-magazine`

