## /SHOP ROUTE STRUCTURE

### URLs
- Index: `/shop`
- Single post: `/shop/[slug]`
- Nested (by category): `/shop/[category]/[slug]`

### File locations
```
src/
├── app/
│   └── shop/
│       ├── page.tsx                  ← shop index, groups posts by category
│       ├── [...slug]/
│       │   └── page.tsx              ← catch-all route, handles all post URLs
│       └── templates/
│           └── ShopTemplate.tsx      ← ONE template for all post types
├── components/
│   └── shop/
│       ├── ShopProductCard.tsx       ← individual product card (grid + featured layouts)
│       ├── ShopProductGrid.tsx       ← renders groups of cards, handles inline injection
│       ├── WinnerBadge.tsx           ← top-pick highlight block (shown below hero)
│       ├── ComparisonTable.tsx       ← side-by-side product comparison table
│       ├── ProsConsBlock.tsx         ← pros/cons per product
│       ├── ShopTableOfContents.tsx   ← sticky sidebar TOC + mobile TOC, auto active tracking
│       ├── ShopInlineCTA.tsx         ← mid-article CTA strip (fires after first content section)
│       ├── ShopFinalCTA.tsx          ← ranked final CTA block, replaces generic conclusion
│       └── ShopFAQ.tsx               ← accordion FAQ, bottom of post
├── lib/
│   └── shop.ts                       ← reads content/shop/, getAllShopPosts(), getShopPost()
├── types/
│   └── shop.ts                       ← ShopPost and ShopProduct TypeScript types
└── content/
    └── shop/
        └── [slug].md or [slug].mdx   ← post files live here
```

