## CONTENT FILES

- Live in `src/content/shop/`
- File format: `.md` (standard) or `.mdx` (if using React components inline)
- Filename = slug: `best-gel-nail-lamps-2025.md` → URL: `/shop/best-gel-nail-lamps-2025`
- Nested: `tools/best-gel-nail-lamps-2025.md` → URL: `/shop/tools/best-gel-nail-lamps-2025`

