## FRONTMATTER — ALL FIELDS

```yaml
---
# ── Required ──────────────────────────────────────────────
title: "Best Gel Nail Lamps in 2025"
excerpt: "We tested 12 UV/LED nail lamps so you don't have to."
date: "2025-06-01"
author: "Mirellé"
category: "Nail Tools"           # shown as label on index + hero
image: "/images/blog/hero.jpg"
imageAlt: "Best nail lamps 2025"

# ── Optional meta ──────────────────────────────────────────
imageWidth: 1200
imageHeight: 630
readTime: "8 min read"
canonical: ""                    # leave blank unless overriding

# ── Post type (SEO/schema hint only, doesn't change layout) ─
postType: "best-of"              # best-of | review | comparison

# ── Conversion components — activate with these flags ───────
winnerIndex: 0                   # index into products[] → activates WinnerBadge + sidebar CTA + ShopInlineCTA
showComparison: true             # renders ComparisonTable
showProscons: true               # renders ProsConsBlock for every product
comparisonCaption: "How the top picks compare"   # optional label above table

# ── Products array ─────────────────────────────────────────
products:
  - name: "Beetles Nail Lamp 48W"
    brand: "Beetles"
    price: "$29.99"
    image: "/images/blog/beetles-lamp.jpg"
    link: "https://amzn.to/xxxxx"        # affiliate link
    badge: "Best Overall"                # shown as label on card + WinnerBadge
    rating: 4.8                          # 1–5, renders star row
    reviewCount: 4200                    # optional, not currently displayed
    details:                             # bullet points shown in featured layout + WinnerBadge
      - "48W dual light source"
      - "Fits full hand including thumb"
    pros:                                # shown in ProsConsBlock (needs showProscons: true)
      - "Fast cure time"
      - "Affordable"
    cons:
      - "Plastic build"

# ── Comparison table (needs showComparison: true) ──────────
comparisonTable:
  features:
    - "Wattage"
    - "Cure Time"
    - "Fits Full Hand"
    - "Auto Sensor"
    - "USB Charging"
  columns:
    - name: "Beetles 48W"          # must match or reference a product
      price: "$29.99"
      link: "https://amzn.to/xxxxx"
      values:
        - "48W"                    # string value for text rows
        - "30–60s"
        - true                     # boolean true → renders checkmark
        - true
        - false                    # boolean false → renders X
    - name: "MelodySusie 54W"
      price: "$45.99"
      link: "https://amzn.to/xxxxx"
      values:
        - "54W"
        - "30–45s"
        - true
        - true
        - true

# ── FAQ (accordion at bottom) ──────────────────────────────
faqs:
  - question: "What wattage do I need?"
    answer: "For home use, 36W–48W is plenty."
  - question: "Are all lamps compatible with all gel brands?"
    answer: "Most are. Check the gel brand's recommendations for specialty formulas."
---
```

