## COMPONENT REFERENCE — WHEN EACH FIRES

| Component | Trigger | Position |
|---|---|---|
| `WinnerBadge` | `winnerIndex` set in frontmatter | Below hero, above content |
| `ShopInlineCTA` | `winnerIndex` set | After first ~30% of content |
| `ComparisonTable` | `showComparison: true` + `comparisonTable` data | After middle content section |
| `ProsConsBlock` | `showProscons: true` | After remaining content, one block per product |
| `ShopFinalCTA` | Always, if products exist | After pros/cons, before FAQ |
| `ShopFAQ` | `faqs` array has entries | Bottom of post, before EEAT |
| `ShopTableOfContents` | Auto — reads H2/H3 from content | Sticky sidebar (desktop) + top (mobile) |
| `ShopProductGrid` | `{{PRODUCTS:n:i}}` placeholder in content | Wherever placed in markdown |
| Sidebar winner card | `winnerIndex` set | Sticky sidebar, below TOC |

