## POST TYPES — WHAT TO SET

### Best-of post (e.g. "10 Best Gel Nail Lamps")
```yaml
postType: "best-of"
winnerIndex: 0
showComparison: true
showProscons: false      # optional for best-of
```
Use `{{PRODUCTS:2:0,1}}` or `{{PRODUCTS:4:0,1,2,3}}` throughout content.

### Review post (single product deep dive)
```yaml
postType: "review"
winnerIndex: 0
showComparison: false
showProscons: true
```
Use `{{PRODUCTS:1:0}}` for featured layout. Include detailed `pros` and `cons`.

### Comparison post (head-to-head)
```yaml
postType: "comparison"
winnerIndex: 0           # the winner of the comparison
showComparison: true
showProscons: true
```
Always include `comparisonTable` data. Use `{{PRODUCTS:2:0,1}}` for head-to-head pairs.

