## WHAT DOES NOT EXIST / NOT TO USE

- No pink/accent colors anywhere in shop components
- No `StickyBottomNav`, `GlassCard`, `PremiumButton` — unused
- Do NOT import from `components/Blog/ProductCard` or `components/Blog/ProductGrid` — those are the old broken versions. Always use `components/shop/` versions.
- No separate templates per post type — one `ShopTemplate.tsx` handles all three
- `postType` field is for schema/SEO hints only, does NOT change which template renders
